{"arkId":"cl010094154","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010094154","modified ":"2025-09-02","title":"Le sacrifice d\u0027Abraham","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Le sacrifice d\u0027Abraham"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1150","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [SCULPT] Salle 201 - Cluny - La sculpture romane au 12e si\u00e8cle","room":"Salle 201, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 0","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1150,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"Milieu du XIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"France Poitou","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 1848","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"chapiteau d\u0027applique","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"0,41","displayDimension":"0,41 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0,785","displayDimension":"0,785 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,44","displayDimension":"0,44 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"pierre calcaire","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"Notre-Dame-de-la-Couldre (France-\u003EParthenay-\u003E\u00e9glise)","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Provient de l\u0027\u00e9glise Notre-Dame-de-la-Couldre \u00e0 Parthenay (Deux-S\u00e8vres), devenue bien national \u00e0 la R\u00e9volution, vendue, et en majeure partie ruin\u00e9e au d\u00e9but du XIXe si\u00e8cle. \r\nChapiteaux utilis\u00e9s en remploi dans la construction du portail d\u0027entr\u00e9e d\u0027une propri\u00e9t\u00e9 contig\u00fce \u00e0 l\u0027\u00e9glise, acquise par les religieuses de la Congr\u00e9gation des Ursulines de J\u00e9sus, de Chavagnes-en-Paillers (Vend\u00e9e), pour y \u00e9tablir une maison d\u0027\u00e9ducation. Etablissement abandonn\u00e9 par les religieuses en 1903. \r\nCongr\u00e9gation dissoute en 1913. Acquis, avec une partie de la propri\u00e9t\u00e9, par Melle N. Guilhaud, directrice de la maison d\u0027\u00e9ducation, en 1914. \r\nCommerce d\u0027art, Paris, 1917 (Charles Joret, puis Joseph Altounian). \r\nCommerce d\u2019art, New York (Arnold Seligmann). \r\nDon Arnold Seligmann, 1925 (comit\u00e9 du 26 f\u00e9vrier 1925, d\u00e9cret du 1er avril 1925).","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Joret, Charles","note":"","role":", Antiquaire \/ Marchand d\u0027art"},{"value":"Altounian, Joseph Alexandre","note":"","role":", Antiquaire \/ Marchand d\u0027art"},{"value":"M. Seligmann, Arnold","note":"","role":", Antiquaire \/ Marchand d\u0027art ; Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"26\/02\/1925","startYear":1925,"endYear":1925},{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"01\/04\/1925","startYear":1925,"endYear":1925}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"material":[{"value":"pierre calcaire"}],"place":[{"value":"Notre-Dame-de-la-Couldre"}],"objectType":[{"value":"chapiteau d\u0027applique"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Maxwell, Robert A., \u00ab Accounting for taste. American collectors and twelfth-century French sculptu